Label: RightOfInformationAndAccess
Text: This privacy statement explains the personal data Microsoft processes, how Microsoft processes it, and for what purposes.
Rationale: This extract identifies the right of individuals to be informed about the processing of their personal data.

Label: RightOfInformationAndAccess
Text: For individuals in the United States, please refer to our U.S. State Data Privacy Notice and the Consumer Health Data Privacy Policy for additional information about the processing of your personal data, and your rights under applicable U.S. State data privacy laws.
Rationale: This indicates that individuals have the right to access information regarding how their personal data is processed and the rights they have under specific laws.

Label: RightOfInformationAndAccess
Text: You can control your personal data that Microsoft has obtained, and exercise your data protection rights, by contacting Microsoft or using various tools we provide.
Rationale: This extract indicates the right to access and control personal data held by Microsoft.

Label: RightOfInformationAndAccess
Text: Access and clear some of your data through the Microsoft privacy dashboard.
Rationale: This extract highlights the ability to access personal data through a specific tool provided by Microsoft.

Label: RightOfInformationAndAccess
Text: Personal data associated with your Microsoft account includes credentials, name and contact data, payment data, device and usage data, your contacts, information about your activities, and your interests and favorites.
Rationale: This extract identifies the types of personal data that users have the right to access.

Label: RightOfInformationAndAccess
Text: You can also learn more about our Enterprise and Developer Products features and settings, including choices that impact your privacy or your end users privacy, in product documentation.
Rationale: This extract indicates that users have the right to access information about the features and settings that affect their privacy.

Label: RightOfInformationAndAccess
Text: we give you choices about the personal data we collect and how we use it.
Rationale: This statement indicates that users have the right to know what data is collected and how it is utilized.

Label: RectificationAndErasure
Text: Parents or guardians can change or revoke the consent choices previously made.
Rationale: This indicates the ability to modify or erase consent related to the child's account.

Label: RectificationAndErasure
Text: The parent or guardian can manage their childs information and settings on their Family Safety page and view and delete a childs data on their privacy dashboard.
Rationale: This shows that parents have the right to view and delete their child's data.

Label: RightToObject
Text: Control the use of your data for personalized advertising from Microsoft by visiting our opt-out page.
Rationale: This extract shows the ability to opt-out of the use of personal data for advertising purposes.

Label: AITraining
Text: As part of our efforts to improve and develop our products, we may use your data to develop and train our AI models.
Rationale: This statement indicates that user data may be utilized for training AI models.

Label: AITraining
Text: Microsofts collection and use of personal data in developing and deploying AI features is consistent with commitments outlined in this privacy statement.
Rationale: This indicates that user data is being utilized for the purpose of training AI features.

Label: AITraining
Text: The main Copilot Pro website and app has similar data collection, use, and controls as consumer Copilot, as described above.
Rationale: This suggests that user data is being used to enhance AI capabilities in different Copilot services.

Label: AITraining
Text: intelligently sense, process, and act on informationlearning and adapting over time.
Rationale: This extract indicates that the AI system learns and adapts over time, which implies the use of user data for AI training.

Label: ContentUploadedOnProducts
Text: Users can start a draft of a new Word document, generate a PowerPoint presentation, quickly find the answers to complex search queries online.
Rationale: This indicates that the content created by users may be utilized by Microsoft in relation to its products.

Label: Cookies
Text: Cookies are small text files placed on your device to store data that can be recalled by a web server in the domain that placed the cookie.
Rationale: This extract explains the use of cookies for data storage and processing.

Label: Cookies
Text: We use cookies and similar technologies for storing and honoring your preferences and settings, enabling you to sign in, providing interest-based advertising, combating fraud, analyzing how our products perform, and fulfilling other legitimate purposes.
Rationale: This extract outlines the various purposes for which cookies are used, indicating data collection practices.

Label: Cookies
Text: Where required, we obtain your consent prior to placing or using optional cookies that are not (i) strictly necessary to provide the website; or (ii) for the purpose of facilitating a communication.
Rationale: This extract specifies the requirement of user consent for using non-essential cookies, highlighting user rights.

Label: OptOut
Text: You have choices when it comes to the technology you use and the data you share. When we ask you to provide personal data, you can decline.
Rationale: This statement indicates that users have the option to decline providing personal data.

Label: OptOut
Text: Control the use of your data for personalized advertising from Microsoft by visiting our opt-out page.
Rationale: This extract explicitly mentions the option to opt-out of personalized advertising, which is a practical right.

Label: OptOut
Text: You have a variety of tools to control the data collected by cookies, web beacons, and similar technologies.
Rationale: This extract informs users about their ability to control and opt-out of data collection through cookies.

Label: UsageByThirdParties
Text: We share your personal data with your consent or to complete any transaction or provide any product you have requested or authorized.
Rationale: This extract indicates that personal data may be shared with third parties based on user consent or for specific transactions.

Label: UsageByThirdParties
Text: We also share data with Microsoft-controlled affiliates and subsidiaries; with vendors working on our behalf; when required by law or to respond to legal process;
Rationale: This extract outlines the sharing of data with various entities, including third parties, which falls under the category of usage by third parties.

Label: UsageByThirdParties
Text: Please note that, as defined under certain U.S. state data privacy laws, 'sharing' also relates to providing personal data to third parties for personalized advertising purposes.
Rationale: This extract clearly states that personal data is shared with third parties for advertising purposes, indicating a use of user data by third parties.

Label: UsageByThirdParties
Text: Third party cookies may include: Social Media cookies designed to show you ads and content based on your social media profiles and activities on our websites.
Rationale: This extract discusses the involvement of third parties in utilizing cookies for targeted advertising.

Label: UsageByThirdParties
Text: If you sign into a service offered by a third party with your Microsoft account, you will share with that third party the account data required by that service.
Rationale: This extract indicates that data may be shared with third parties when using their services.

Label: UsageByThirdParties
Text: The Enterprise and Developer Products enable you to purchase, subscribe to, or use other products and online services from Microsoft or third parties with different privacy practices, and those other products and online services are governed by their respective privacy statements and policies.
Rationale: This extract highlights that third-party services will have their own privacy practices, indicating the usage of user data by third parties.

Label: UsageByThirdParties
Text: your organization may use centralized management tools provided by Microsoft or others to access and process your data
Rationale: This indicates that third parties (organizations) may use tools to access and process user data.
